document.full_text: australia's qantas airways  plans to axe capacity and management jobs and retire some aircraft early under cost-cutting measures aimed at offsetting soaring fuel prices and the impact of natural disasters in japan, new zealand and australia.
document.title: qantas to cut capacity, reduce management to offset fuel
